originalText.text: I had a great experience using Move NYC Real Estate. From my first interaction with Norris, I felt comfortable, as he walked me through the complete process. He then had a meeting with myself and Anthony, where they both listened to my top priorities that I was looking for, for my first home.  They sent me a few houses that met my family’s needs that night. I am happy to say that my husband and I closed on our home yesterday, and it was the first home that they showed us. I totally recommend them. Anthony was amazing!

originalText.text:
Jeremy Williams, Move NYC Realtor was very helpful in my search
for a new apartment. He answered every question and returned every
phone call in a timely fashion. He was patience in educating me on
obtaining the proper paper work to successfully apply for a apartment.
Move NYC unit listings is top notch. Jeremy showed me four apartments
in one day. I liked every unit. If you would like a stress free experience when apartment hunting I highly recommend Jeremy and Move NYC.
I'm in a wonderful new home and I'm grateful to Jeremy for his help.

originalText.text: Tiffany Daniels made my moving experience easier. She helped find me a new apartment within my budget on limited time. Absolutely professional and thorough she was super friendly and communication was great. She was always available and made me feel as if I was her only client. I can honestly say Tiffany Daniels was the best real estate agent that I have dealt with to date.

originalText.text: Going through the home buying process would have be far more stressful had it not been for the hard work of Norris' team. My agent in particular her name was Tiffany Daniels, and she was astounding. Hard working, a tough bargain maker, her tenacity is unmatched. She has great connections and was a valuable resource on my team for the past year. The world of real estate is a tough environment but with a person like Ms. Daniels working for you, you can't fail at getting the home of your dreams. If I had to either do it again or find another home in the future I will be coming back to Tiffany.

originalText.text: Both Tiffany Daniels and Norris James were a pleasure to work with. Tiffany was extremely responsive. I would show her a house, she would contact the seller's agent that day and we would visit the house the day after. They always assured me that I would find a house that I loved and they helped me get it ! Even when I started to slow down in the search process, they would send me the new listed properties and follow up with me to make sure I didn't want to see any other properties. Tiffany and Norris would contact everyone involved in my housing transaction to ensure that we would close in a timely manner. I truly appreciate both of them and would recommend them to anyone who is looking to purchase a home.
